All Classes and Interfaces

Classes
Class
Description
Barrier
The Barrier class represents the separation between every tile of the game board.
BarrierHorizontal
The BarrierHorizontal class is a sub class of the Barrier class and inherit of all its methods and attributes.
BarrierVertical
The BarrierVertical class is a sub class of the Barrier class and inherit of all its methods and attributes.
Board
The Board class represents the game board with everything on it : tiles, barriers and players.
Main
 
Player
The Player class is used to create a player object to use on the board, it inherits from the Circle class with all its attributes and methods.
Tile
The Tile class is used to create a tile of the board on which you can place the players, it inherits from the Rectangle class from javafx.
